Generic single-database configuration
Initialize Alembic -> alembic init migrations
Generate a New Migration -> alembic revision -m "Describe migration change here"
Apply Migrations (Upgrade the Database) -> alembic upgrade head
View Current Database Version-> alembic current
viev migration history -> alembic history
Show Pending Migrations -> alembic heads
Reset Database Migrations (Use with Caution!) ->alembic downgrade base , alembic upgrade head
